name: Sound Is Energy PRE-ORDER
description:
Releases November 11th, 2008. Pre-order and there's no shipping costs. This is my collaborative E.P. with Dizz. Album produced by Leonard and Dizz. Features original beats by Leonard, Motion Plus, The Devout, and Snowman. Original artwork by David Burner (a.k.a. Toast).
Tracklisting... 1. We're Glad It's You (INTRO) 2. Keep Listening (FT. TOAST) 3. Is What It Is (INTERLUDE) 4. Are You Who You Are? 5. Change The World 6. No Clue (INTERLUDE) 7. Once Upon... 8. Sound Is Energy (FT. SNOWMAN, TOAST) 9. Mustard Seed (OUTRO)

name: Leonard Button Pack!
description:
Is your jacket, backpack, or grandma missing some flair? Just add a Leonard button to make it (or her) a little bit more exciting! 4 1" buttons come in this pack. Designs are (from left to right): Green Light Bulb, Blue Boombox, Yellow Sleepy Cat, and Red B-Boys. Enjoy!
The Official Leonard myspace site.
Think Twice Buttons. They make some mighty fine buttons.
